    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n9596" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χανδάνω</span></b>  (root <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χαδ</span>, cf. pre-hendo), ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐχάνδανον, χάνδανε</span>, fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χείσεται</span>, aor. 2 <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔχαδε,
            χάδε</span>, inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-έειν</span>, perf.
          part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεχανδότα</span>, plup. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεχάνδει</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">hold, contain</span>, of
          the capacity of vessels, etc., <i><span class="en">Il.
            23.742</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">. ρ 344</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            4.96</span></i>; fig., of capacity of shouting, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὅσον κεφαλή χάδε φωτός</span>, as loud as a man's ‘head holds,’
          as loud as human voice is capable of shouting, <i><span class="en">Il. 11.462</span></i>; fig., also <i><span class="en">Il. 4.24</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            8.461</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
